          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV",
                "STTA",
                "EXTB",
                "GSPEC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ".4-5 Sanple sandwiches and",
                "several monitor and absorber foils were irradiated at",
                "beam current of about 100Na.3 Staks were irradiated",
                "at julich cyclotron with 25 MeV incident energy",
                "degradated from 47 +- 0.2 Mev primary deuteron energy.",
                "2 stacks were irradiated at cv-28 cyclotron with 13.4",
                "MeV primary energy. The energy degradation was",
                "calculated according to C.F. Williamson et Al. Cea-",
                "r3042(1966) the decay data were taken from C.M.Lederer",
                "and V.S.Shirley, table of isotopes, Willey, new york",
                " (1988) and C. Brownie and r.B.Friestone, table of",
                "radioactive isotopes, Willey, New York (1986)."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "31.4% Enriched (1 mg/cm**2) Se-74 was electrodeposited",
                "on Al foils covered by an other thin Al foil."
              ]
            }
          ],
